            "heading": "You Wear Croydon",
            "paragraphs": [
                "Artist Samia Tossio invites children to create wearable “architectural hats” representing Croydon landmarks or other famous buildings, or imaginary towers, or skylines, using recycled and upcycled materials. We will provide easy print-outs of Croydon specific, London specific, and famous London buildings for younger children and discuss simple building types and structural basics, providing materials for medium skill level participants to make their own from scratch."
